PrecisEnactment of the EXPORT OF SUBSTANCES UNDER THE ROTTERDAM CONVENTION REGULATIONS - which are designed to ensure that chemicals and pesticides subject to the Prior Informed Consent (PIC) procedure are not exported to a Party to the Rotterdam Convention unless it has provided its consent to the shipment, and establish the conditions applicable to the exportation of substances listed on Schedule 3 to the Act.
